GSD.description:
btrfs: do not WARN_ON() if we have PageError set

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.16.13 by commit 9efcc83b33b576302147634eca9bece8e3737e34. For more details please see the references link.
